Sharp work from Raza as he swooped down on the ball..

commentary: Junaid Khan to Chibhabha, 5 runs good length and on middle, tucked to short midwicket for one. The fielder (Malik) swoops down on the ball and misses the direct hit at the non-strikers'. Two fielders converge on the ball but the ball eludes both and runs away to the boundary. Chibhabha gets off the mark with five as the umpire got in way of the fielders. Junaid too could't get back near the stumps in time
